cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.MM 

The paper deals with feature extraction from digital pathology whole slide images using deep learning techniques. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also proposes a self-supervised learning method, which involves training a siamese network, and this falls under the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The paper also involves measuring image retrieval and descriptor pair distance ratio, which falls under the information retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories.
